OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Charles
OL,4,CGiles
OL,6,FCharles Giles, Age: 101, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 19 February 2024
OL,10,FSpending the entire war on HMS
OL,11,FBleasdale, Mr Giles had already taken
OL,12,Fpart in the ill-fated Dieppe raid in
OL,13,Fwhich the Allies tried to take control
OL,14,Fof an operational port in occupied
OL,15,FFrance.
OL,17,FA Hunt-class destroyer, Bleasdale had
OL,18,Fbeen involved in a series of exercises
OL,19,Fto prepare for Neptune, the
OL,20,Foperational name for the sea invasion.
