OL,4,CGiles
OL,6,F"Not the exact one he was on, it was
OL,7,Fthe Cavalier, he lit up when he went
OL,8,Fon that ship.
OL,10,F"The pride you could see he had of
OL,11,Fbeing able to go there was amazing."
